<SYNC Start=5338><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, hey! How was your audition?
<SYNC Start=8171><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=8775><P Class=ENCC>
I'm sorry, do I know you?
<SYNC Start=10902><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
