<SYNC Start=181646><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182415><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, well, don't ruin it.<br>Just play along, at least.
<SYNC Start=186715><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=186920><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. Sorry.
<SYNC Start=188854><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=190456><P Class=ENCC>
We have to throw her a shower?
<SYNC Start=192549><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=198164><P Class=ENCC>
What'd you decide to do<br>about the movie?
<SYNC Start=200724><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=200967><P Class=ENCC>
I don't know.
<SYNC Start=202298><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=203469><P Class=ENCC>
