<SYNC Start=210173><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=210376><P Class=ENCC>
That's what you say about porn.
<SYNC Start=212537><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=213446><P Class=ENCC>
