<SYNC Start=321982><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=327327><P Class=ENCC>
I'm glad we decided not to sleep<br>together before the wedding.
<SYNC Start=330888><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331397><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, boy. Me too.
<SYNC Start=333194><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=333966><P Class=ENCC>
I was thinking, say we had a big fight,<br>and broke up for a few hours.
<SYNC Start=339029><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=339372><P Class=ENCC>
Technically, we could have sex again.
<SYNC Start=342500><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344043><P Class=ENCC>
