<SYNC Start=349341><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=349549><P Class=ENCC>
That's me. Come on.
<SYNC Start=350880><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=351150><P Class=ENCC>
Wait. Cassie's in the guest room.<br>We're going to lunch.
<SYNC Start=354517><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=354721><P Class=ENCC>
Get rid of her, obsessive and shrill!
<SYNC Start=356848><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
