Shrill? The wedding is back on.
<SYNC Start=360321><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=362662><P Class=ENCC>
I thought I heard voices.<br>You must be Chandler.
<SYNC Start=365859><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=366532><P Class=ENCC>
