<SYNC Start=393054><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=395428><P Class=ENCC>
-Cassie needs to stay at your place.<br>-Why?
<SYNC Start=398022><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=398231><P Class=ENCC>
