<SYNC Start=445478><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, great.
<SYNC Start=446911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=447880><P Class=ENCC>
I'd have been perfect for this part.
<SYNC Start=450246><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=450450><P Class=ENCC>
You made a bad decision and<br>ruined your movie. Good day!
<SYNC Start=453886><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=454187><P Class=ENCC>
You didn't need to come, because the<br>director saw your tape and loved it.
<SYNC Start=458954><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=461427><P Class=ENCC>
End scene.
<SYNC Start=463520><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=465665><P Class=ENCC>
Wasn't that fun? We did<br>a little improv there. Yeah!
<SYNC Start=470193><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=471471><P Class=ENCC>
So, you were saying?
<SYNC Start=473132><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=473406><P Class=ENCC>
