Wow! Sure! That's great.
<SYNC Start=478302><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=478511><P Class=ENCC>
Your agent said you're okay<br>with nudity.
<SYNC Start=480775><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480980><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, sure. As long as<br>it's handled tastefully.
<SYNC Start=484108><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=484350><P Class=ENCC>
And that barn is not too cold.
<SYNC Start=486682><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489789><P Class=ENCC>
Perfect. There's one more thing.
<SYNC Start=492053><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=492291><P Class=ENCC>
