<SYNC Start=611544><P Class=ENCC>
fashion.
<SYNC Start=612772><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=616849><P Class=ENCC>
-Like what?<br>-Well, I'm not sure yet.
<SYNC Start=619943><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=620152><P Class=ENCC>
Off the top of my head,<br>I'm thinking...
<SYNC Start=623144><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=623456><P Class=ENCC>
